{"tid":1460960,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣818大遊行","createTime":"2019-08-13T05:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:49:38.000Z","uid":170652,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"6d013f5d0b084e94b778fcf229d3fb94e4239a46","tid":1460960,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"民陣記招講818大遊行<br />\n真心覺得要再做一次好多好多好多人嘅大遊行<br />\n民陣終於出手<br />\n好希望前線，和理非，左膠，非建制嘅人全部都一齊參與<br />\n近期嘅運動基礎係200萬人都無回應<br />\n我地真係好需要再有一個好實際嘅畫面話俾人知<br />\n成個運動有好多民意基礎<br />\n希望大家完左遊行就返屋企或者集會<br />\n總之目標係集人<br />\n之後要煲大件事<br />\n希望嗰日大家唔會以暴力升級行動<br />\n因為好多家庭有大有細好想出嚟支持<br />\n會怕升級行動令老人家小朋友受傷唔出嚟<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">目標清晰集人</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">目標清晰集人</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">目標清晰集人</span></span><br />\n核爆我都唔會割蓆<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f144c9818911472b3ce58796c4587e2b6dbf93","tid":1460960,"uid":294974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"76e7f33f9a5a84874955e047e124d9b96810ec71","tid":1460960,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"cdfeee7e666e73f0a189fed70765fbab35d11088","tid":1460960,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:38:40.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"40c714d23e7ad69b22de35f57b3cea2603a57bf3","tid":1460960,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"a2ba4ec053dd47b13bd3d579e580dacbb7a619be","tid":1460960,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:39:20.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"6c750336387289ca8b8c0893a9cf5f44c04142b3","tid":1460960,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:39:42.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"f369b85c3bf346a7d4e38f6fff0738887457d354","tid":1460960,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:39:48.000Z","msg":"3球<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740561728c0c7bf929e756677d37c6dbda78cd04","tid":1460960,"uid":21170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"斷你十連"},{"pid":"75c019c9b10dcdf9795042faeb1fdde62b241bd7","tid":1460960,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:40:09.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"e65ef88fa6a1c66bacea5763df9f8b0fc59668f7","tid":1460960,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"740561728c0c7bf929e756677d37c6dbda78cd04","tid":1460960,"uid":21170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"斷你十連"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9b0217883bfba5498e22d82cecf8c5deb837b7","tid":1460960,"uid":21170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e65ef88fa6a1c66bacea5763df9f8b0fc59668f7","tid":1460960,"uid":170652,"like":